{"id":275533,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/global-voices-照片集：巴基斯坦全国各地抗议活动和平收场/","date":"2013-01-21T09:00:13Z","modified":"2013-01-21T09:00:13Z","title":"Global Voices | 照片集：巴基斯坦全国各地抗议活动和平收场","content":"<p><p>巴基斯坦全国一百多个城市支持什叶派的抗议活动<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://dawn.com/2013/01/14/sit-in-3/\">终于结束</a>了。抗议的动机来自2013年一月十日发生在西南部奎达市哈札拉什叶社区，造成超过百人遇害的<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2013/01/11/pakistani-activist-khudi-ali-killed-in-bombings-targeting-hazaras/\">爆炸事件</a>。</p>\n<p>这起爆炸是巴基斯坦西南部俾路支省历史上血腥的一天。非法武装团体<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://tribune.com.pk/story/7139/ten-dead-in-quetta-blast/\">强戈维军声称这起恐怖罪行是他们的手笔</a>。</p>\n<p>攻击发生后，奎达哈札拉社区的成员集结至阿拉姆达路，开始和平静坐抗议。当他们伴着亲人棺木坐在冰冷雨中的照片在社群网站上流传开来，<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2013/01/13/we-are-all-hazara-protests-across-pakistan/\">支持他们的和平静坐抗议</a>也如野火燎原般在全国各地展开。来自各个教派部族的巴基斯坦人，携手谴责打着伊斯兰名义的恐怖活动。</p>\n<p>奎达的抗议群众只有一个要求：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>让奎达市纳入巴基斯坦军队的控制之下，并采取省长直接统治。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>政府花了四天处理这些事务，尔后长达四天的和平静坐总算告一段落。死者家属在要求得到回应前拒绝将亲人遗体下葬，如今遇难者终于可以入土为安。</p>\n<p>巴基斯坦全国各地的民众纷纷发起静坐活动，抗议场地包括主要铁路路线和高速公路。据报导，登记有案的静坐活动在<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://en.shiapost.com/2013/01/13/shitte-protests-witnessed-over-100-cities-across-pakistan/\">超过一百个城镇</a>举行，甚至在入夜后气温仅有零下十四度的锡卡都也有民众参与静坐。他们的目的很单纯：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>接受奎达抗议群众的要求。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>以下是巴基斯坦主要城市的抗议活动照片：</p>\n<p><strong>喀拉蚩</strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<div><img title=\"Bilawal_House Protest\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/BAgoALCCcAEXrLq1-375x281.jpg\" alt=\"Protest infront of Bilawal House against Shia Killing.\" width=\"375\" height=\"281\" /></p>\n<p>人民党总部前抗议杀害什叶派民众的人群。来源：<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/ArsalanMKhan/status/290526159375069186/photo/1\">‏@ArsalanMKhan</a></p>\n</div>\n<div><img title=\"pic2\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/pic2-375x281.jpg\" alt=\"Protest infront of Bilawal House against Shia Killing. Source: FacebookSyed Sabih Abbass Rizvi</a>. Copyight: Used with author&#8217;s permission&#8221; width=&#8221;375&#8243; height=&#8221;281&#8243; /></p>\n<p>人民党总部前抗议杀害什叶派民众的人群。照片经授权使用。版权：<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/razvi572\">FacebookSyed Sabih Abbass Rizvi</a>。</p>\n</div>\n<p><div><img title=\"BAgKv7MCYAAVbl31\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/BAgKv7MCYAAVbl31-375x281.jpg\" alt=\"Protest at Karachi Press Club.\" width=\"375\" height=\"281\" /></p>\n<p>喀拉蚩媒体俱乐部前的抗议活动。来源：<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/faisalkapadia/status/290493994419511296/photo/1\">@‏faisalkapadia</a></p>\n</div>\n<div><img title=\"BAjyvtlCMAIIalg1\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/BAjyvtlCMAIIalg1-375x281.jpg\" alt=\"A child during a protest near Numaish Chowrangi.\" width=\"375\" height=\"281\" /></p>\n<p>努马伊什丘朗吉附近的抗议活动中的孩童。来源：<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/i/#%21/arifaBatool/media/slideshow?url=pic.twitter.com%2F7xAFOnb2\">@arifaBatool</a></p>\n</div>\n<p>这是一段喀拉蚩努马伊什抗议活动的<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://vimeo.com/57285088\">影片</a>：</p>\n<h3><strong>海得拉巴</strong></h3>\n<div><img title=\"BAgjLItCMAA8VZh\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/BAgjLItCMAA8VZh4-375x250.jpg\" alt=\"Protest near Hyderabad Bypass.\" width=\"375\" height=\"250\" /></p>\n<p>海得拉巴快速道路旁的抗议活动。来源：<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/ImZeesh/status/290478615299248128\">@ImZeesh</a></p>\n</div>\n<h3><span><strong>拉合尔</strong></span></h3>\n<div><img title=\"716616572\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/716616572-375x280.jpg\" alt=\"#WeAreAllHazara protests in Lahore.\" width=\"375\" height=\"280\" /></p>\n<p>拉合尔的#WeAreAllHazara抗议活动。时间：凌晨两点。来源：<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/XumarShirazi/status/290198155230842880\">@XumarShirazi</a></p>\n</div>\n<div><img title=\"717093926\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/717093926-375x280.jpg\" alt=\"Protest infront of Governor House Lahore. Time: 11:30 pm.\" width=\"375\" height=\"280\" /></p>\n<p>拉合尔省长办公室前的抗议活动。时间：晚上十一点半。来源：Qurrat-ul -in Haider (<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/mojesma/status/290533479156969473\">‏@mojesma</a>)</p>\n</div>\n<div><img title=\"BAgjLItCMAA8VZh\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/BAgjLItCMAA8VZh-333x300.jpg\" alt=\"A young Shia girl asking her \"Sunni Brothers\" to join the protest.\" width=\"333\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p>一名年轻什叶派少女请求“逊尼派的兄弟”加入抗议活动。来源：<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/annyzaidi/status/290520850178912257\">‏@annyzaidi</a></p>\n</div>\n<div><img title=\"BAgjLItCMAA8VZh\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/BAgjLItCMAA8VZh2-375x250.jpg\" alt=\"Sit in continues all night.\" width=\"375\" height=\"250\" /></p>\n<p>彻夜静坐的群众。来源：<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=578632015484877&#038;set=a.361414720539942.105527.358515214163226&#038;type=1&#038;permPage=1\">FaceBookTaimour Mubashar</a></p>\n</div>\n<h3><strong>伊斯兰玛巴德</strong></h3>\n<div><img title=\"BAgjLItCMAA8VZh\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/BAgjLItCMAA8VZh3-375x211.jpg\" alt=\"Women and children during a peaceful sit-in.\" width=\"375\" height=\"211\" /></p>\n<p>和平静坐的女性和儿童。来源：‏<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/Zulfi25/status/290530738124767232\">@Zulfi25</a></p>\n</div>\n<div><img title=\"BAgjLItCMAA8VZh\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/BAgjLItCMAA8VZh7-375x281.jpg\" alt=\"Trying their best to fight the cold climate.\" width=\"375\" height=\"281\" /></p>\n<p>民众努力底御寒冷。来源：<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/Mehr_Shah/status/290641897599410176\">@Mehr_Shah</a></p>\n</div>\n<h3><strong>白沙瓦</strong></h3>\n<div><img title=\"BAgjLItCMAA8VZh\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/BAgjLItCMAA8VZh5-375x281.jpg\" alt=\"A youngster participates in the protest.\" width=\"375\" height=\"281\" /></p>\n<p>参加抗议活动的小孩。来源：‏<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/Khushal/status/290533969483681792\">@Khushal</a></p>\n</div>\n<div><img title=\"BAgjLItCMAA8VZh\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/BAgjLItCMAA8VZh6-375x210.jpg\" alt=\"Peshawar Sit-in.\" width=\"375\" height=\"210\" /></p>\n<p>白沙瓦静坐活动。来源：Hassan Turi (‏<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/spin_ghar/status/290440224809574400\">@spin_ghar</a>)</p>\n</div>\n<h3><strong>奎达</strong></h3>\n<div><img title=\"BAgjLItCMAA8VZh\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/BAgjLItCMAA8VZh8-375x281.jpg\" alt=\"People sitting in Quetta with the cadaver of their loved ones.\" width=\"375\" height=\"281\" /></p>\n<p>在亲人遗体旁静坐的民众。来源：Humayoun Behzad (‏<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/behzadjee/status/290550255878012928\">@behzadjee</a>)</p>\n</div>\n<div><img title=\"BAgjLItCMAA8VZh\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/BAgjLItCMAA8VZh9-375x281.jpg\" alt=\"Hunger strike organized by Hazara Development Party (HDP) in Quetta. \" width=\"375\" height=\"281\" /></p>\n<p>哈札拉发展党（HDP）在奎达举行绝食抗议。来源：Humayoun Behzad (‏<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/behzadjee/status/290548838878547969\">@behzadjee</a>)</p>\n</div>\n<div><img title=\"BAgjLItCMAA8VZh\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/BAgjLItCMAA8VZh12-375x281.jpg\" alt=\"People sitting firm. Night temperature in Quetta stays below zero degree centigrade. \" width=\"375\" height=\"281\" /></p>\n<p>坚持静坐的民众。奎达入夜后气温低于零度。来源：Humayoun Behzad (‏<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/behzadjee/status/290275876816433153\">@behzadjee</a>)</p>\n</div>\n<div>校对者：Ameli</div>\n<p><span><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/kumail/\" title=\"文章导读 Kumail Ahmed\">Kumail Ahmed</a></span> · <span>译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.gl